textDisplay: I actually had a vivid dream or possible foresight about this before COVID reached the US. I was in my bed in my own room and from a close distance to the living room , I could clearly hear the tv and my parents talking over it in a very troubling tone; what the anchor of my local news said  to this day shocked me to my core “ this new surge now surpassed the 9 million mark of fatalities” this dream was so vivid and it ended then after . I had this dream sometime before this coverage took place. After that I went to work, not putting any thoughts on what I just dreamt. But when I watch this report on my phone I looked up on the sunset and felt this sudden change in the air around me, the type you get when you know your life is about to change forever.
